OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will remain dry with some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells on Saturday,
OL,7,Fbut sunshine will be quite hazy with
OL,8,Fhigh level cloud. Fresh to strong
OL,9,Fsoutherly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,12,Fclear spells. Remaining dry overnight
OL,13,Fwith any lingering cloud clearing to
OL,14,Fgive largely clear skies. Fresh
OL,15,Fsoutherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
