OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA dry and clear start to the
OL,6,Fday, but cloud building through the
OL,7,Fmorning. Remaining dry and mostly
OL,8,Fcloudy in the afternoon with some
OL,9,Fbright intervals. Fresh southerly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fon Monday with outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fpossible. Bright spells Tuesday with
OL,15,Fshowers possible. Rain spreads
OL,16,Feastwards later Tuesday as winds
OL,17,Fstrengthen. Rain clearing to bright
OL,18,Fspells and showers Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
